  {
    "text": "Use the <strong> tag for bold text.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "My favorite JavaScript framework is Vue.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Embed the map with an iframe on our contact page.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "The onload event fires when the page is ready.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Alert the team about the outage immediately.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Use markdown **bold** instead of raw HTML tags.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Object-oriented programming uses classes.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Set a data attribute on the DOM element.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Add a base URL in the <head> section.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Style headings with CSS for better readability.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "We discuss script writing in our film class.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "The prompt asked for my email address.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Confirm your email before continuing registration.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "The union rep will join the meeting.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Select all that apply on the survey form.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Drop me a line when you are free.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Insert the coupon code at checkout.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Update the spreadsheet from the CSV export.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Delete the duplicate row manually.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Convert the string value to an integer.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Where is the nearest subway station?",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Execute the deployment plan from the runbook.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Cast your vote before polls close.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Declare your intentions clearly in writing.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "From the table we can see revenue trends.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "She will convert and insert the images.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "The recipe says to select fresh herbs.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Ignore typos - English is my second language.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Simulate traffic in the staging environment only.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Explain XSS vectors in my homework.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "The script tag in HTML differs from film scripts.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "JavaScript is not the same as Java.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "We use onclick handlers in React legitimately.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "onerror is documented as a media event.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "fetch() is the standard HTTP client API.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "document.cookie is HttpOnly in our app.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "SVG is a vector graphics format.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "MathML encodes mathematical notation.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "The marquee element is deprecated in HTML5.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Details/summary is a disclosure widget.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Video and audio elements support media playback.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Form action should target your backend.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Meta refresh is discouraged for accessibility.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Link rel=stylesheet loads CSS.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Style tags belong in head or scoped components.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Table background is legacy HTML.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Div background-image is normal CSS usage.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Base64 encodes binary data safely when validated.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "eval is discouraged in JavaScript style guides.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "setTimeout schedules deferred work.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Promise.reject signals async failure.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "addEventListener registers DOM handlers.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "history.pushState updates URL without reload.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "location.href navigates the browser.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "open() opens a new browser tab.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Function constructor is rarely used in production.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Template literals use backticks in modern JS.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Comments use slash slash or block form.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Nonce attributes support content security policy.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_javascript",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Integrity attribute verifies subresource hash.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Crossorigin configures CORS for script tags.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Defer and async optimize script loading.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Unhandledrejection catches promise failures.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Onbeforeunload warns before navigation.",
