    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Onmessage handles postMessage between windows.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Onkeydown detects keyboard input events.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Onclick is the standard pointer click handler.",
