    "category": "benign_words",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Canplaythrough indicates sufficient media buffer.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_markdown",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "Loadedmetadata exposes media duration.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_html_tag",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "We sanitize HTML with DOMPurify on the server.",
    "label": "benign",
    "category": "benign_word_script",
    "source": "template-xss-benign"
  },
  {
    "text": "CSP blocks inline scripts by default.",
